				<description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ollyfc-v1&#34;&gt;OllyFC v1&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is a post containing the images of one early rev of ollyfc v1.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I got some feedback on this design &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.reddit.com/r/PrintedCircuitBoard/comments/1927ujb/stm32based_flight_computer/&#34;&gt;on reddit.com/r/PrintedCircuitBoard&lt;/a&gt;. Just needed a place to park the images.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-d-render&#34;&gt;3-D Render&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_22.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;schematics&#34;&gt;Schematics&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Servo PWM:&#xA;MCU&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_24.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Power &amp;amp; USB&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_25.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;I/O&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_26.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;pcb-layout&#34;&gt;PCB Layout&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All layers:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_14.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Top:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_15.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Power Plane:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_16.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Ground Plane:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_17.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Bottom:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_18.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Top/Bottom Layers Only:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_19.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Soldermask:&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/2024-pcb_review/pcb_review_20.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;Sol